ique website with all 21 of your uploaded product photos, priced between <s=
trong>KSh 1,000=E2=80=932,500</strong>. Here's what's included:</div><h2>Pr=
oduct Catalog (21 Handbags)</h2><div class=3D"paragraph">Each product uses =
your actual uploaded images with:</div><ul start=3D"1"><li><div class=3D"pa=
ragraph"><strong>Realistic pricing</strong> (KSh 1,000=E2=80=932,500 range)=
</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Original prices</strong> sh=
own with strikethrough for perceived value</div></li><li><div class=3D"para=
graph"><strong>Descriptive names</strong> based on bag styles (Crossbody, T=
ote, Bucket, Satchel, etc.)</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>=
Category badges</strong> like "Best Seller", "New", "Trending", "Premium"</=
div></li></ul><h2 class=3D"">Features Implemented</h2><h3 class=3D"">1. <st=
rong>Closet Sidebar</strong> =F0=9F=9B=8D</h3><ul start=3D"1"><li><div clas=
s=3D"paragraph">Slide-out panel from the right</div></li><li><div class=3D"=
paragraph">Live item count badge on the header button</div></li><li><div cl=
ass=3D"paragraph">Item thumbnails, names, categories, and prices</div></li>=
<li><div class=3D"paragraph">Running total + checkout button</div></li><li>=
<div class=3D"paragraph">One-click remove functionality</div></li><li><div =
class=3D"paragraph">Empty state with friendly messaging</div></li></ul><h3>=
2. <strong>Backend Persistence</strong> (Simulated)</h3><ul start=3D"1"><li=
><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Sign In/Out</strong> modal with demo cred=
entials pre-filled</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph">When logged in: c=
loset syncs to "server" (localStorage per user)</div></li><li><div class=3D=
"paragraph">When logged out: works offline with localStorage fallback</div>=
</li><li><div class=3D"paragraph">Smart merge on login =E2=80=94 combines l=
ocal + server closets without duplicates</div></li></ul><h3>3. <strong clas=
s=3D"">Filtering &amp; Sorting</strong></h3><ul start=3D"1"><li><div class=
=3D"paragraph"><strong>Sort by</strong>: Featured, Price (Low/High), Name (=
A-Z/Z-A)</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Style filter</stron=
g>: Dynamic checkboxes for all bag categories (Tote, Crossbody, Shoulder, B=
ucket, Satchel, Hobo, Tote Sets)</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><st=
rong>Price range slider</strong>: KSh 1,000=E2=80=932,500 with live display=
</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Active filter tags</strong>=
 with one-click removal</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Clea=
r All</strong> button</div></li></ul><h2>Design Highlights</h2><ul start=3D=
"1"><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong class=3D"">Luxury aesthetic</stron=
g> with gold accents and elegant serif typography</div></li><li><div class=
=3D"paragraph"><strong class=3D"">Hero banner</strong> with brand tagline</=
div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong>Hover animations</strong> on =
product cards (lift + image zoom)</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><s=
trong>Toast notifications</strong> instead of alerts</div></li><li><div cla=
ss=3D"paragraph"><strong>Responsive</strong> =E2=80=94 sidebar stacks on mo=
bile, closet goes full-width</div></li><li><div class=3D"paragraph"><strong=
>Image fallbacks</strong> if any photo fails to load</div></li></ul><h2>To =
Use Your Photos</h2><div class=3D"paragraph">The code references your uploa=
